Product Name: Babyliss 6604 E Le Pro Light Hair Dryer / 2000 W  Italy
Product Description: -Among the relatively inexpensive hairdryers there are professional models. Their main advantage is reliability and increased working life. If you want to buy a similar hair dryer, pay attention to BaByliss 6604E.Professional solutions at homeBaByliss 6604E is part of the Pro AC series, which the manufacturer positions as a professional. However, its functionality is the same as for household models: two speeds and three temperature regimes, the supply of cold air. As a drawback, it can be noted the lack of ionization, which is present in many household phenes in 2015.6604E favorably differs from the "home" hair dryer engine of professional quality with a power of 2000 watts. What advantages does it give? First, the engine provides a high speed air flow (90 km / h), which will help to dry your wet hair more quickly. Secondly, the service life (1000 hours), according to the manufacturer, four times exceeds the resource of classic hair dryers. And an objective "plus" is an extended warranty period of 3 years.Styling as a hairdresserAnother fen is distinguished by a very thin concentrator (6x76 mm). Therefore, it creates a focused and intense airflow. Therefore, the 6604E is ideal for those who use the hair dryer more often for styling than for drying. Otherwise, it is worth paying attention to models with a larger tip width.BaByliss 6604E with a powerful professional engine and a narrow nozzle is best for hair styling.

Product Name: Nikon D850 DSLR Camera - Body Only
Product Description:
-Single-Point AF: The camera uses a single point to find focus. 
-Dynamic-Area AF: Available with 25, 72, or 153-point selections, this mode uses a primary single focus point to lock onto focus, and then makes use of the surrounding points for maintaining focus while tracking erratically-moving subjects. 
-Group-Area AF: This mode treats smaller groups of AF points as a single point for a wider field of recognition, and is well-suited to tracking faces or other detailed subjects. 
-3D-Tracking: Using a subject's color information, this mode utilizes all 153 points to maintain focus on a moving subject while half-pressing the shutter button. 
-Auto-Area AF: This mode makes use of all 153 points to quickly identify the main subject, and then prioritizes recognized faces as portrait subjects in any AF servo mode.

-Although not essentially a lubricant, garages are regularly used to lubricate all light machinery and electrical equipment. 
-Protects metal from rust and corrosion or fail parts, repels moisture and simply lubricates everything. It is great when it comes to cleaning out grease, dirt and other marks from most surfaces. 
-Lubricant is a mixture of chemical concentrates in a high quality petroleum distillate. It can’t be used not on textiles, rubber or plastic. 
-Its operating temperature is between 100 ° C and + 500 ° F. 
-Highly recommended to clean, preserve and protect all tools. 
-The main functions: 
-Clean: cleanse dirt, stains and grease. It dissolves adhesives, allowing easy removal of labels, tape and stickers. 
-Protection: protects metal surfaces with corrosion-resistant ingredients to protect against moisture and other corrosive elements. 
-Penetration: solves rust-to-metal bindings and frees stuck, frozen or rusty metal parts 
-Displaces moisture: dries quickly on electrical equipment to eliminate moisture-induced short circuit, (remember to turn on power before you spray)
